race.comment: CENTU CAVADDI (2) is clearly the horse to beat. The debut win at Donald was strong before being given a chance in a good 3yo race at Sandown Hillside and running on strongly to grab third behind Navy Pilot. He unfortunately missed a run in the G1 Caulfield Guineas when given an each-way hope and this is clearly a much easier target. REGAL AWARD (3) comes through the same race behind Navy Pilot when doing plenty wrong in running as favourite. Out to 1600m now suits much better, look for a better run. OBVIOUS (7) won his maiden in quick time at Bendigo when last seen over 1500m, winning well. Drawn ideally here and can measure up. TAGLINE (1) has won his past couple in easier company and deserves a crack at these.
